metadata.name: MetaSoco #Germany
metadata.description:
MetaSoco is a collection of 3,200 digital, 100 for each team, the NFT values of all teams will fluctuate in real time with each game's performance.

MetaSoco is one of the NFT project of Aether metaverse, which provides a web3 metaverse platform for football fans around the world to socialize and play together.
